{"tid":2294471,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"CCTVB廣告金主《寵物藥妝》原來係暗黃 叫手足見字飲水","createTime":"2020-11-21T04:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T17:58:34.000Z","uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9581c52540255feeef3124621916c081635558e8","tid":2294471,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"藍屍見到好擺買<br />\n寵物藥妝落重廣告嘅愛回家<br />\n邊個引個黃店入黎賣黑暴文化架<br />\n要嚴肅處理 呢單嘢比之前手套更過分<br />\n<br />\n不過wats pet一日未停廣告 <br />\n大家繼續入去俾嬲<br />\n同時幫手提醒藍屍呢間野係港獨黑暴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uK91ErX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuK91ErX.png&h=5cca186b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/1UlRZunPfo/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F1UlRZunPfo%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=f76a7390\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/1UlRZunPfo/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watspetmacyhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatspetmacyhk%2F&d=HaoFMq3H8OfxnxI562yM3%2B2wegjmRFMzjbv%2B285MJ7g%3D&h=37cf1ebd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watspetmacyhk/</a>"},{"pid":"4a7555e6cddee0f31dcf9cba16b47154e665dbb8","tid":2294471,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da43a9e99f74358d9f41d117fb01a16373690a7","tid":2294471,"uid":125026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T05:14:12.000Z","msg":"宜家先知見字飲水係黃絲專用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5815c6fcc7b64d5f4a09e6cf7d6e98f175696581","tid":2294471,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7da43a9e99f74358d9f41d117fb01a16373690a7","tid":2294471,"uid